<br>
I don't think whole guilds will move.  Those that think all the &quot;uber guilds&quot; will jump on it are mistaken about the importance of the price tag.  I'd guess only 10% of the players in any given uber guild could afford it.  I suspect the culture will be very odd at first with a bunch of high level folks that really don't know anyone.  I could work out great, but it will definitely be something new.<br>
<br>
I'm ambivalent on the web-page issue.  On the one hand, it can attract the &quot;loot bragarts&quot; and on the other, it's very useful for trading.  Just click on over to your page to find out what gear you have.  If you can inspect your own bank and make your page entirely private, that would be ideal.  Just have to wait and see how that turns out.<br>
<br>
The kind of folks I'd be worried might harm the culture there are those that can't afford it, but go there anyway.  Those folks will be extremely loud and obnoxious if everything doesn't go absolutely perfect -- after all, they're paying this &quot;incredibly high price&quot; for premium service. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/umelmell.showPublicProfile?language=EN>melmell</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.theorderofthedragon.com/docs/fanart/cross.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>A_Idiot_666</span><br>  Posts: 165<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/2/02 8:57:47 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1259.topic&index=42>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.jesus-is-lord.com/ozzy.gif height=102 width=74></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ..</span><hr size=1> ok. i wanna compare a couple things.... tholuxe paells usually has a event every, ummm.. 3-4 months? i've gone to the halloween one, i've been to the story-at-the-tunnel thing too... i've seen firiona vie in gfay and Firiona Vie (=P).. i've seen the undead invasion in EC, i've seen lotta stuff.... ok like i said, these events are very rare. and my oppinion on them?.. they stink.. most plots are repeated and end up being ruined. i hate it. so i don't attend them anymore.. ok... now DAILY gm events?.. omg. i ain't even gonna go there. if they can't set up a rare 3-4 month gm event decently then plz guess how these are suppose to be?.. also is it gonna be a pattern.. <br>
